<p>Alleged attack on, and stabbing of, a prominent blogger in Dhaka. 
According to the information received, on 14 January 2013, Mr. Asif 
Mohiuddin was attacked by three unidentified men as he was leaving his 
office in Uttara district. He was stabbed several times in the neck and back 
and was in critical condition at the time of sending the communication. Mr. 
Mohiuddin is a prominent blogger, whose Bengali language blog &#8213;Almighty 
</p>
