<p>Alleged imminent execution of five representatives of the Ahwazi Arab 
minority. According to the information received, Messrs. Mohammad Ali 
Amouri, Sayed Jaber Alboshoka, Sayed Mokhtar Alboshoka, Hashem 
Sha&#8216;bani Amouri, and Hadi Rashidi (or Rashedi), all representatives of the 
</p>
