Bay where he remains. Mr. Suleiman&#8216;s health is rapidly deteriorating. He is 
reportedly suffering from severe pain in the area of his kidneys and appendix. Mr. 
Suleiman was examined by a doctor and had x-rays taken. Despite his repeated 
complaints, he has allegedly not received adequate medical attention.  
